<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Cambria Portal</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1e293b;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
        }
        .container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #1d4ed8);
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
        }
        .logo svg {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            color: white;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #1e293b;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0 0 12px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b, #475569);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #1e293b;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #475569;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .credentials-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f1f5f9, #e2e8f0);
            border: 2px solid #cbd5e1;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 32px 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .credentials-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #10b981, #059669);
        }
        .credential-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .credential-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .credential-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #64748b;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            min-width: 120px;
            margin-right: 16px;
        }
        .credential-value {
            font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Monaco', 'Inconsolata', 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e293b;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            flex: 1;
            box-shadow: inset 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
        }
        .role-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #4f46e5);
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-left: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        .features-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff, #e0f2fe);
            border: 1px solid #0ea5e9;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        .features-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0c4a6e;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .features-icon {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
        .features-list {
            color: #0c4a6e;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .features-list li {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        .login-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #1d4ed8);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 18px 36px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            min-width: 200px;
        }
        .login-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #1e40af);
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 32px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .footer-text {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .contact-info {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .security-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dcfce7, #bbf7d0);
            color: #166534;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .security-badge svg {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            margin-right: 6px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h1>Welcome to Cambria Portal</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Your account has been successfully created</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">Hello {{userName}},</p>
            
            <p class="message">
                Welcome to the Cambria Portal! Your account has been successfully created and you now have access to our comprehensive client management system. 
                Below are your login credentials to get started:
            </p>

            <div class="credentials-section">
                <div class="credential-row">
                    <div class="credential-label">Email</div>
                    <div class="credential-value">{{userEmail}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="credential-row">
                    <div class="credential-label">Password</div>
                    <div class="credential-value">{{password}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="credential-row">
                    <div class="credential-label">Role</div>
                    <div class="credential-value">{{userRole}} User</div>
                    <div class="role-badge">{{userRole}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="features-section">
                <div class="features-title">
                    <svg class="features-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    What You Can Do
                </div>
                <ul class="features-list">
                    <li>Access client dashboards and reports</li>
                    <li>View and manage client data</li>
                    <li>Upload and organize files</li>
                    <li>Generate monthly reports</li>
                    <li>Track client performance metrics</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="login-button">
                    Get Started
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="security-badge">
                <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
                </svg>
                Secure & Encrypted
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p class="footer-text">
                If you have any questions about your account or need assistance getting started, 
                please contact your system administrator or refer to the user guide.
            </p>
            <p class="contact-info">
                This is an automated message from the Cambria Portal system.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 
